These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, whist
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, orange
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, malaysian
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, volleyball
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the social-worker is the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Game      | whist        | monopoly |
| Color          | orange  | apricot     |
| Transport         | motorbike    | airplane         |
| Job           | analyst    | social-worker |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | malaysian     |
| Pet           | horse      | chinchilla    |
| Sport         | volleyball | golf          |

