The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, social-worker
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, trance
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, russian
2 different pets are kept: goat, mouse
There 2 different types of food: lemon, onion
1. the russian is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Cigar         | montecristo      | dunhill       |
| Job           | entrepreneur | social-worker |
| Flower   | amaryllis      | azalea        |
| Music-Genre   | folk         | trance        |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | russian       |
| Pet           | mouse        | goat          |
| Food     | onion          | lemon    |

