.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, pomegranate
2 different games are played: scrabble, chess
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, teacher
House: ranch-style, townhouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | soy-milk  |
| Food          | pomegranate   | lettuce   |
| Game         | chess | scrabble   |
| Job           | dancer        | teacher   |
| House   | townhouse      | ranch-style |
| Sport         | ice-hockey    | climbing  |
| Movie-Genre     | horror       | sports      |

